font-size:10.0000pt;" >2、为什么要用ajax:</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;
font-size:10.0000pt;" ><br></span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;
