mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >正确答案：</font> Ajax应用程序的优势在于:</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >1. 通过异步模式,提升了用户体验</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >2. 优化了浏览器和服务器之间的传输,减少不必要的数据往返,减少了带宽占用</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >3. Ajax引擎在客户端运行,承担了一部分本来由服务器承担的工作,从而减少了大用户量下的服务器负载。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >2、AJAX最大的特点是什么。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Ajax可以实现动态不刷新(局部刷新)</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >就是能在不更新整个页面的前提下维护数据。这使得</font>Web应用程序更为迅捷地回应用户动作,并避免了在网络上发送那些没有改变过的信息。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >}</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=18  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;
font-size:10.0000pt;" >3、请介绍一下XMLhttprequest对象。</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;
font-size:10.0000pt;" ><br></span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;
font-size:10.0000pt;" >{</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >正确答案：</font> Ajax的核心是JavaScript对象XmlHttpRequest。该对象在Internet Explorer 5中首次引入,它是一种支持异步请求的技术。简而言之,XmlHttpRequest使您可以使用JavaScript向服务器提出请求并处理响应,而不阻塞用户。通过XMLHttpRequest对象,Web开发人员可以在页面加载以后进行页面的局部更新。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >}</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=18  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;
